"or delete a snippet, click the snippet type that interests you. Clicking "
"the snippet type takes you to the edit screen, from which you can add, "
"edit, or delete a snippet. Hovering over an individual snippet displays "
"the options to edit or delete that snippet. To add a new snippet to the "
